org.hps.readout.util

Class TriggerTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.readout.util.TriggerTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TriggerTime>

    public class TriggerTime
extends Object
implements Comparable<TriggerTime>
    Class TriggerTime stores the time at which a trigger occurs in terms of simulation time, and also the triggering driver is tracked.
